OUR DEGREE SUSTAINABILIT Y FRAMEWORK

7.4 Task Force on ClimateRelated Financial Disclosures (TCFD)

Our strategic response to climate-related opportunities and risks The DEGREE sustainability framework includes the sustain-

ability-related topics important for Siemens, including decarbonization and resource efficiency, for which we have set ambitious targets (see paragraph “Metrics and targets”). These targets, in conjunction with our overall Science-Based Targets initiative-validated (SBTi) decarbonization target, apply to Siemens’ own operations and to our upstream and downstream value chain.